			<h1>Updates: v1.3 Released <span class="author">Fang Liu</span></h1>

			<p>
				We are pleased to annouce a new version of MRiLab, MRiLab v1.3, for performing fast and versatile numerical MRI simulation, with new featrues including:
			</p>
			<p>
				<ul>
					<li> Support multi-pool exchange tissue model </li>
					<li> Provide simulation in batch mode </li>
					<li> Provide spatial SAR and power evaluation </li>
					<li> Polish graphical interface</li>
					<li> More... </li>
				</ul>
			</p>
			<p>
				The methods for implementing updates of the numerical simulator can be found at this scientific paper:
				
			</p>
			<p>
			F. Liu, J.V. Velikina, W.F. Block, R. Kijowski, A.A. Samsonov. <i>Fast Realistic MRI Simulations Based on Generalized Multi-Pool Exchange Tissue Model.</i> IEEE Transactions on Medical Imaging. 2016. doi: 10.1109/TMI.2016.2620961
			</p>
			<span><a href="../news.html" class="more">Back to News</a></span>
		</div>
